Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:59.62,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Kato's the tenth most common \Nfamily name in Japan, you know.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:00.96,DefaultTop,Kato,0,0,0,,{Your point is?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.57,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I just barely win.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:06.85,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Since Kumogakure is within the top nine \Nmost common family names in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.42,DefaultTop,Kato,0,0,0,,{No, I really doubt that.}
